{"tid":528922,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲古城同文物都係好深地底挖掘出來 係咪代表人類越住越高地平線？","createTime":"2018-01-14T11:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T17:22:12.000Z","uid":49004,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ccdee2ac50cb71f0ea3cf2c8547bdcb05ce4f8b5","tid":528922,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"例如暴雨令河水泛濫淹沒 或山泥傾瀉埋沒 幾十億年動物屍體堆積的fossil fuel <br />\n例如科學家發掘出土地乜乜層代表乜乜紀時期發生變異 導致大滅絕等等泥土堆積再堆積<br />\n<br />\n令人類居住環境愈來愈高地平線<br />\n<br />\n可能我地企緊嘅土地(填海唔計)<br />\n幾千年前係個山丘水平 但埋沒咗<br />\n<br />\n所以部份土地未來幾百年內被海水淹沒係正常事<br />\n唔關全球暖化事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鳩問 only <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64260bba0e8841d56a0e511edfc35a03e71d4fbf","tid":528922,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:15:55.000Z","msg":"開post冇人理 睇嚟好多人block咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌"},{"pid":"028d98671fb843c877a95e7a501c9e828a4cbc39","tid":528922,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"好多古城都拆咗再建 被發現嘅都係有d原因先可以保留 明唔明"},{"pid":"a6f7ab49cbc39182e92b80be1ee2cba644b6bdf1","tid":528922,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:21:36.000Z","msg":"因為地表會自動適應全球暖化<br />\n當水平面愈高<br />\n地面就會愈高"},{"pid":"acfd463afc4986856621f6873278677c58b8ba25","tid":528922,"uid":42374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:23:48.000Z","msg":"經歷幾千幾萬年沉積會褶曲同抬升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a918a5dd32ac39922d5e8dda0ec4b55bf7ba327","tid":528922,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"028d98